title: PSIP Pemalang
text:
PSIP Pemalang is an Indonesian <a href="association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Pemalang">Pemalang</a>, <a href="Central%20Java">Central Java</a>. PSIP currently competes in <a href="Liga%203%20%28Indonesia%29">Liga 3</a>. Their nickname is "Laskar Benowo" and "<a href="Dhole">Ajag</a> <a href="Java%20Island">Jawa</a>"
History.
Founded in 1970. In 2018, PSIP won the <a href="2018%20Liga%203%20Central%20Java">2018 Liga 3 Central Java</a> after beating their rival, <a href="Persibara%20Banjarnegara">Persibara Banjarnegara</a>. In <a href="2018%E2%80%9319%20Piala%20Indonesia">2018–19 Piala Indonesia</a>, this club made it into the round of 64.
Supporters.
PSIP has 2 base of supporters namely Lasbo Mania and Ultras LBS.
